Pivot Tables
- It is an Excel features to summarize, analyze and rearrange the data.
- It privides an interactive way to calculate, aggregrate and and analyze data.
Operations :
- summarizing 
- Filtering 
- calculating percentage
- Grouping the data

Pivot Chart
- It is an extension of a PivotTable that provids a graphical representation of the data summarized in the PivotTable
Operations :
- Changing Chart Types
- Customizing Chart Elements
- Drilling Down Data

Power Query
- It is a data collection technology that discover, conect, combine and refine data.
- I provides import, clean and transform the data.
Operations :
- Merging Queries
- Appending Queries
- Unpivoting Columns 
- Creating Calculated Columns
